column5: ANyone have any idea as to the value of this lure? It has been identified as a Paw Paw Wottafrog.

Theres one on E-Bay going for $120.oo, heres the link: http://cgi.ebay.ca/VINTAGE-PAW-PAW-WOTTAFR...1742.m153.l1262 I also did a google search and found some of them for $20.00 i guess it depends on the condition of the lure.
Here's another one...from an vintage fishing site....  http://www.goantiques.com/detail,paw-paw-wotta,552972.html  They are selling it for $79 USD  Very cool looking lure!
